#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "cereal in milk"
msgid_plural "cereal in milks"
msgstr[0] "牛奶麥片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cereal in milk'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Cereal in milk! It's grrrreat!"
msgstr "牛奶麥片！簡直太棒了！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "chocolatey cereal"
msgid_plural "chocolatey cereals"
msgstr[0] "巧克力麥片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chocolatey cereal'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "A box of chocolate puff ball cereal. They'll make you coocoo!"
msgstr "一盒巧克力泡芙球麥片。它們會讓你變得瘋狂！"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "almonds"
msgid_plural "almonds"
msgstr[0] "杏仁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'almonds', 'str_pl': 'almonds'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"One of the most versatile nuts out there, almonds are good both for snacking"
" and cooking. These are plain."
msgstr "杏仁是最多才多藝的堅果之一，既適合當零食也適合烹飪。這些是原味的。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "pecans"
msgid_plural "pecans"
msgstr[0] "山核桃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pecans', 'str_pl': 'pecans'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "Ah, pecans. The crown jewel of nuts! These are plain."
msgstr "啊，山核桃。堅果中的瑰寶！這些是原味的。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "walnuts"
msgid_plural "walnuts"
msgstr[0] "核桃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'walnuts', 'str_pl': 'walnuts'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A dark, brain-shaped nut that is vaguely meat-like in flavor. These are "
"plain."
msgstr "一種深色、腦狀的堅果，味道隱約類似肉類。這些是原味的。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "cashews"
msgid_plural "cashews"
msgstr[0] "腰果"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cashews', 'str_pl': 'cashews'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Lung-shaped nuts that are a staple of any good trail mix. These are plain."
msgstr "肺狀的堅果，是任何優質混合零食的必備品。這些是原味的。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "peanuts"
msgid_plural "peanuts"
msgstr[0] "花生"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'peanuts', 'str_pl': 'peanuts'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"The iconic peanut. Bland by itself, but amazing in cooking! These are plain."
msgstr "標誌性的花生。本身味道平淡，但在烹飪中卻非常出色！這些是原味的。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "nut milk"
msgid_plural "nut milks"
msgstr[0] "堅果奶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nut milk', 'str_pl': 'nut milks'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"Milk from nuts. Very good for you, but very bland-tasting. Will keep "
"forever."
msgstr "由堅果製成的奶。對健康非常有益，但味道非常平淡。可以永久保存。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "nut paste"
msgid_plural "nut pastes"
msgstr[0] "堅果醬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nut paste', 'str_pl': 'nut pastes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"The ground up soaked flesh of nuts after milk processing. Definitely not "
"very appetizing in its current form."
msgstr "堅果經過浸泡、制奶後磨碎的果肉。目前這種形態絕對不太開胃。"

#: .\comestibles.json
msgid "trail mix"
msgid_plural "trail mixes"
msgstr[0] "混合零食"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'trail mix', 'str_pl': 'trail mixes'}
#: .\comestibles.json
msgid ""
"A mix of chopped and whole nuts, chocolate, and either sweet or salty "
"seasoning. Good for your health!"
msgstr "由切碎和完整的堅果、巧克力以及甜味或鹹味調味料混合而成。對健康有益！"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "ceramic bowl with lid"
msgid_plural "ceramic bowl with lids"
msgstr[0] "帶蓋陶瓷碗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceramic bowl with lid'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
"A shallow dessert bowl with an improvised plastic lid. Can be used as a "
"container or as a tool. Holds 250 ml of liquid."
msgstr "一個淺口甜點碗，配有臨時塑料蓋。可用作容器或工具。可容納250毫升液體。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "glass bowl with lid"
msgid_plural "glass bowl with lids"
msgstr[0] "帶蓋玻璃碗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'glass bowl with lid'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
"A glass dessert bowl with an improvised plastic lid. Can be used as a "
"container or as a tool. Holds 250 ml of liquid."
msgstr "一個玻璃甜點碗，配有臨時塑料蓋。可用作容器或工具。可容納250毫升液體。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "plastic bowl with lid"
msgid_plural "plastic bowl with lids"
msgstr[0] "帶蓋塑料碗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plastic bowl with lid'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
"A plastic bowl with an improvised plastic lid.  Can be used as a container "
"or as a tool.  Holds 250 ml of liquid."
msgstr "一個塑料碗，配有臨時塑料蓋。可用作容器或工具。可容納250毫升液體。"

#: .\containers.json
msgid "pewter bowl with lid"
msgid_plural "pewter bowl with lids"
msgstr[0] "帶蓋白鑞碗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pewter bowl with lid'}
#: .\containers.json
msgid ""
"A pewter bowl with an improvised plastic lid.  Can be used as a container or"
" as a tool.  Holds 250 ml of liquid."
msgstr "一個白鑞碗，配有臨時塑料蓋。可用作容器或工具。可容納250毫升液體。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "The Glory Of Cereal!"
msgstr "穀物榮耀！"

#. ~ Description for The Glory Of Cereal!
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds cereal in milk as a thing. Also adds 5 types of nuts, the ability to "
"make non-spoil nut milk, and a separate healthier nut milk cereal."
msgstr "新增牛奶穀物食品。同時添加5種堅果、製作不易變質的堅果奶的能力，以及一種更健康的獨立堅果奶穀物。"
